{
  "stem": "766.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We should survive and we should do the job.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So besides the supply of food which we got, we got an extra [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH], I don't know what to say-- an extra, let's say, for each doctor and the family so that the doctor should be able to work.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A ration, yeah-- a supplement, I would call it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't too much, but it's still-- everything counted.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He got also-- because he also was an asset for the German.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They knew him because the few which had something to do with the war machine, to say-- because they need the hospital and everything.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah, now I remind myself-- in the ghetto, I was called my brother to the KRIPO-- that's Kriminalpolizei-- that somebody reported to them-- they talked to me that I have diamonds.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] And I should give it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And before, I had a little golden bracelet, a little-- so I gave it to a friend who knew somebody from the KRIPO to tell them that this I have and that's all.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But later, when they took me to the real interrogation, I said, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My father is dead, or it's 1933.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We never were very rich people and I only came here-- I had to pass examinations in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I am only a beginner.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't have anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They didn't touch me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I want to say I was never beaten by a German.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It means I am-- maybe other doctors also not.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I was lucky.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "On my own skin, I didn't feel it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But when I was in the KRIPO and he interrogated me-- so he wanted to catch me, which I said the truth-- I didn't have to-- that they asked me that I am married.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
